title: Introducing The World's First STREET LEGAL Lamborghini Super Trofeo Evo - Unicorn V4 [4K UHD]
author: Alex Choi
description:
Here is the result of 2 years of my dedication, and countless people's passion and devotion who had nothing but faith in me. Not a lot of people will understand what it takes to do a massive build like this. Yes, this is the same car as the monkey bars. V3 was simply a cocoon. It's good to be back.
